metadata.name: Benkei - Blademaid - #003
metadata.description:
CATGIRLS DOMINATION PROJECT - #003

Benkei is a warrior forever in battle! When she isn't repelling invaders attempting to cross the bridge to her Lord's estate, she can be found indoors battling dirty laundry, dust bunnies and unwashed dishes.  She often gets her weapons mixed up but has since become equally dangerous with a broom as she is with her blades!

Design by:
Jessica Luna & Pepperoni Creative Center

Artwork and animation by:
Jessica Luna

Adobe Photoshop
2300 x 2300px
